WEBVTT

00:00.968 --> 00:02.403
male announcer: IN THE
CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:02.436 --> 00:04.038
SEXUALLY BASED OFFENSES

00:04.072 --> 00:06.774
ARE CONSIDERED
ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:06.807 --> 00:09.110
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:09.143 --> 00:11.145
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:11.179 --> 00:13.114
ARE MEMBERS
OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:13.147 --> 00:14.582
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:14.615 --> 00:17.051
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:19.520 --> 00:22.423
- I'M STARTING A PETITION
TO FORCE THIS PLACE TO GO GREEN.

00:22.456 --> 00:23.691
- DON'T ROCK THE BOAT,
FRANKIE.

00:23.724 --> 00:25.159
- BUT I READ ONLINE THAT

00:25.193 --> 00:27.061
THE CHEMICALS THEY USE HERE
CAUSE THE BIG C.

00:27.095 --> 00:30.198
- AND THE THREE PACKS A DAY YOU
SMOKE AIN'T DOING YOU NO HARM.

00:31.865 --> 00:33.834
- WHOA, WHOA, WHOA!
- STOP THE LINE, YOU IDIOT.

00:33.867 --> 00:36.137
[click, alarm blares]

00:36.170 --> 00:39.840
- FEMALE, EARLY 20s.
SERIOUS VAGINAL TRAUMA.

00:39.873 --> 00:41.542
UP TOP'S JUST AS BAD.

00:41.575 --> 00:42.810
- PRACTICALLY
CUT HER HEAD OFF.

00:42.843 --> 00:45.113
- JUGULAR AND CAROTID
WERE SEVERED.

00:45.146 --> 00:46.214
C.O.D.'S EXSANGUINATION.

00:46.247 --> 00:49.683
- WHERE ARE THE FIVE PINTS OF
BLOOD SHE'S MISSING?

00:49.717 --> 00:50.884
- NO ONE FOUND IT ON SITE.

00:50.918 --> 00:53.287
OF COURSE, IF SOMEBODY HERE
HAD DIRTY LAUNDRY TO CLEAN,

00:53.321 --> 00:55.089
THERE WOULD BE NO PROBLEM.

00:55.123 --> 00:57.125
- SHE'S GOT SMALL CUTS
AND PUNCTURE WOUNDS

00:57.158 --> 00:59.493
ALL OVER HER BREASTS,
STOMACH, AND PELVIC AREA.

00:59.527 --> 01:01.229
THIS GUY'S A REAL SADIST.

01:01.262 --> 01:03.097
- WHAT'S WITH THE BINDINGS?
WHAT ARE THOSE?

01:03.131 --> 01:05.233
- LOOKS LIKE SILK-WRAPPED
ELECTRICAL CORD...

01:05.266 --> 01:06.800
FANCY DECORATORS USE.

01:06.834 --> 01:10.104
- TIME OF DEATH?
- RIGOR'S ALMOST DISSIPATED.

01:10.138 --> 01:11.205
I'D SAY TWO DAYS AGO.

01:11.239 --> 01:12.406
I'LL KNOW MORE
AFTER THE AUTOPSY.

01:12.440 --> 01:14.208
- ANYONE HERE
RECOGNIZE HER?

01:14.242 --> 01:16.244
- SUPERVISOR SAYS
SHE'S NOT AN EMPLOYEE.

01:16.277 --> 01:19.513
AND SHE WANTS TO KNOW WHEN SHE
CAN START THE MACHINES AGAIN.

01:19.547 --> 01:21.215
- DO WE KNOW
WHERE THE LOAD CAME FROM?

01:21.249 --> 01:23.351
- MERCY HOSPITAL.

01:23.384 --> 01:26.254
- THIS WAS NO MERCY KILLING.

02:18.506 --> 02:20.608
- THOSE OFFICERS SAID
I HAD TO TALK TO SVU.

02:20.641 --> 02:22.643
SO WHAT THE HELL DID I DO?
- RAPED AND MURDERED THE GIRL

02:22.676 --> 02:24.312
THAT YOU DROPPED OFF
AT THE LAUNDRY THIS MORNING.

02:24.345 --> 02:25.646
- YOU'VE GOT
THE WRONG GUY.

02:25.679 --> 02:29.783
- LET'S TALK ABOUT IT
AT THE PRECINCT.

02:29.817 --> 02:32.786
- WAIT. W-WAS SHE
IN THE LOAD FROM MERCY?

02:32.820 --> 02:35.623
- OH, FUNNY THAT YOU
WOULD KNOW THAT.

02:35.656 --> 02:38.259
- LISTEN, ALL I DID THERE
WAS SIGN OFF ON THREE CARTS.

02:38.292 --> 02:40.728
THE GUY ROLLED THEM OUT FOR ME
WHILE I HIT THE HEAD.

02:40.761 --> 02:42.530
- WHAT TIME WAS THAT?

02:42.563 --> 02:44.632
- AROUND 4:30 THIS MORNING.
- THEN HOW COME YOU DIDN'T

02:44.665 --> 02:48.236
MAKE YOUR NEXT PICKUP ONLY
FIVE BLOCKS AWAY UNTIL 5:22?

02:48.269 --> 02:49.703
GOT BLADDER PROBLEMS?

02:49.737 --> 02:51.705
- IF YOU THINK I KILLED HER,
YOU'RE CRAZY.

02:51.739 --> 02:53.541
- SAYS THE GUY
WHO WANTS US TO BELIEVE

02:53.574 --> 02:54.875
HE TOOK A 50-MINUTE LEAK.

02:54.908 --> 02:57.878
- OKAY, MY GIRLFRIEND JANICE
IS A NURSE AT MERCY.

02:57.911 --> 02:59.980
I POPPED IN TO SAY HI.

03:00.013 --> 03:01.415
IT WAS A LITTLE SLOW.

03:01.449 --> 03:03.317
WE DUCKED INTO AN EMPTY ROOM,
TO, UH...

03:03.351 --> 03:04.885
- PLAY DOCTOR?

03:04.918 --> 03:07.421
- I SWEAR,
I DIDN'T HURT ANYBODY.

03:07.455 --> 03:09.890
I JUST WANTED TO GET LAID.

03:09.923 --> 03:11.859
- I WAS ON BREAK AT 4:30.

03:11.892 --> 03:14.395
- GETTING PORKED
BY YOUR BOYFRIEND.

03:14.428 --> 03:15.929
- ANOTHER NURSE
WAS COVERING FOR ME.

03:15.963 --> 03:18.266
I DIDN'T ENDANGER
ANY OF MY PATIENTS.

03:18.299 --> 03:20.601
- LIKE THIS ONE?
- SHE WASN'T MINE.

03:20.634 --> 03:22.236
- WOULD YOUR BOYFRIEND HAVE

03:22.270 --> 03:23.637
HAULED OUT A CORPSE
FOR ANYONE ELSE?

03:23.671 --> 03:24.938
- NOT KNOWINGLY.

03:24.972 --> 03:28.409
BUT JOE IN HOUSEKEEPING
HANDLES OVERNIGHT LAUNDRY.

03:28.442 --> 03:30.778
KIND OF A CREEP.
MAYBE HE DUMPED THE BODY.

03:30.811 --> 03:32.713
- LOVEBIRDS WEREN'T LYING.

03:32.746 --> 03:33.814
JOE WAS ALL ALONE
WITH THE CART.

03:33.847 --> 03:36.584
- SCHEDULE SAYS THAT LOAD OF
LAUNDRY CAME FROM PEDES.

03:36.617 --> 03:38.752
NO WAY OUR JANE DOE
WAS A PATIENT THERE.

03:38.786 --> 03:40.988
- MORGUE MISSING ANY BODIES?

03:41.021 --> 03:42.923
- ALL DBs
PRESENT AND ACCOUNTED FOR.

03:42.956 --> 03:44.592
- HOLD ON,
WHAT'S THIS GUY DOING?

03:44.625 --> 03:45.859
- HOW THE HELL'D I MISS THAT?

03:45.893 --> 03:47.395
- MAYBE YOU WERE
ON A DOUGHNUT RUN.

03:47.428 --> 03:49.263
[cell phone rings]
- KILLER WAS DRIVING AROUND

03:49.297 --> 03:50.431
LOOKING FOR
THE PERFECT DUMP SITE.

03:50.464 --> 03:53.801
THEN HE HITS THE JACKPOT:
AN UNATTENDED LAUNDRY TRUCK.

03:53.834 --> 03:55.903
- CAN YOU SEE THE PLATES?
- STABLER.

03:55.936 --> 03:57.538
- ANGLE'S ALL WRONG.

03:57.571 --> 03:59.673
- OKAY, A CAR THAT BOXY
HAS TO BE AN OLD VOLVO,

03:59.707 --> 04:01.875
AND ONLY HALF OF NEW YORK
ARE DRIVING THEM.

04:01.909 --> 04:03.844
IT'S GONNA BE HARD
TO I.D. THE OWNER.

04:03.877 --> 04:06.046
- WELL, WE JUST GOT BETTER LUCK
WITH OUR VICTIM.

04:06.079 --> 04:08.382
- SAMANTHA MILLERTON, 23.

04:08.416 --> 04:09.850
- WHY IS SHE IN THE SYSTEM?

04:09.883 --> 04:12.620
- LOITERING, RESISTING ARREST.
MAINLY POLITICAL RALLIES.

04:12.653 --> 04:13.987
- LATEST COLLAR
WAS FOR TRESPASSING

04:14.021 --> 04:15.389
AT THE GLOBE OIL HEADQUARTERS.

04:15.423 --> 04:17.958
PROBABLY PROTESTING
THEIR LATEST OIL SPILL.

04:17.991 --> 04:20.060
- SHE WORKED FOR
AN ENVIRONMENTAL GROUP?

04:20.093 --> 04:21.962
- YEAH, IT'S AN OUTFIT CALLED
C.L.E.A.N.

04:21.995 --> 04:24.298
COLLECTIVE LIVING ENVIRONMENT
OF ARTISTS FOR NATURE.

04:24.332 --> 04:27.535
WORKS OUT OF AN OLD FACTORY
ON THE LOWER EAST SIDE.

04:30.070 --> 04:33.641
ANY CORPORATE TARGETS ESPECIALLY
UNHAPPY WITH YOUR ARTWORK?

04:33.674 --> 04:35.042
- ALL OF THEM.

04:35.075 --> 04:36.977
BUT GLOBE OIL WENT BALLISTIC.

04:37.010 --> 04:38.712
- HOW SO?

04:38.746 --> 04:41.949
- I FILMED THIS DURING
OUR LAST PROTEST THERE.

04:41.982 --> 04:45.986
THAT'S GLOBE OIL'S SLIMY CEO,
NICHOLAS TURNER.

04:46.019 --> 04:49.089
- GET AWAY FROM ME!
STOP FILMING, NOW!

04:49.122 --> 04:51.959
- NOT UNTIL YOU PAY TO CLEAN UP
THE HUNDREDS OF MILES

04:51.992 --> 04:54.895
OF VIRGIN WILDERNESS
POLLUTED BY YOUR OIL SPILL.

04:54.928 --> 04:58.065
- I PREFER TO GET THE TRASH
OFF MY OWN PROPERTY FIRST.

04:58.098 --> 05:00.568
COLLECT THE GARBAGE.

05:00.601 --> 05:04.572
[scuffling, protesters shouting]

05:04.605 --> 05:08.041
- I'M GONNA SHOW THE WORLD WHAT
YOU'RE REALLY MADE OF, TURNER!

05:08.075 --> 05:09.743
- WHAT WAS SAMANTHA
GOING TO SHOW THE WORLD?

05:09.777 --> 05:10.778
- AN EFFIGY OF TURNER,

05:10.811 --> 05:13.881
MADE OUT OF CRAP SHE FOUND
FROM HIS OWN TRASH.

05:13.914 --> 05:18.419
NICHOLAS TURNER EMBODIES
THE EXCESSES OF THE SUPER-RICH.

05:18.452 --> 05:20.053
THE FRAME
IS MADE FROM HIS EMPTY

05:20.087 --> 05:22.089
CHATEAU LAFITE-ROTHSCHILD
WINE CRATES.

05:22.122 --> 05:25.893
- SILK PAJAMA BOTTOMS STUFFED
WITH THE WALL STREET JOURNAL.

05:25.926 --> 05:28.362
NOW, WHY THROW OUT
THE ITALIAN LOAFERS?

05:28.396 --> 05:31.064
THEY LOOK BRAND-NEW.
- THEY'RE SLIGHTLY SCUFFED.

05:31.098 --> 05:34.067
- OH, A VIAGRA BOTTLE
IN TURNER'S NAME.

05:34.101 --> 05:35.903
OH, FOR HIS NOSE.
I GET THAT.

05:35.936 --> 05:37.571
IT'S NICE.

05:37.605 --> 05:39.940
- SAM WAS GOING TO DOUSE THIS
IN GLOBE OIL GASOLINE

05:39.973 --> 05:42.710
AND LIGHT IT ON FIRE
AT OUR NEXT RALLY.

05:42.743 --> 05:44.044
- AND, UH, NO MOUTH,

05:44.077 --> 05:45.779
BECAUSE SHE WAS TIRED
OF HEARING TURNER'S LIES?

05:45.813 --> 05:47.815
- SHE HADN'T FOUND THE PERFECT
PIECE OF GARBAGE YET.

05:47.848 --> 05:49.717
- MAYBE SHE DID.
AT TURNER'S HOUSE.

05:49.750 --> 05:51.952
SILK-WRAPPED
PINK ELECTRICAL CORDS

05:51.985 --> 05:54.722
WOULD MAKE
A PERFECT PAIR OF LIPS.

05:54.755 --> 05:56.657
- WHAT, DO YOU THINK
HE CAUGHT HER IN THE ACT

05:56.690 --> 05:58.025
AND WANTED TO
TEACH HER A LESSON?

05:58.058 --> 06:00.060
- THAT'S WIRING
FROM TWO LAMPS

06:00.093 --> 06:02.129
MY WIFE HAS
IN HER DRESSING ROOM.

06:02.162 --> 06:04.732
ONE BROKE,
SO I TOSSED THEM.

06:04.765 --> 06:07.167
YOU CAN'T POSSIBLY THINK
I MURDERED THAT GIRL.

06:07.200 --> 06:08.769
- WELL, WE HAVE IT
ON GOOD AUTHORITY

06:08.802 --> 06:10.938
THAT SHE WAS AT YOUR PLACE
THE NIGHT SHE WAS MURDERED.

06:10.971 --> 06:13.641
- I GOT HOME AROUND 2:00 A.M.
AFTER A FUNDRAISER

06:13.674 --> 06:16.944
AND FOUND THAT TERRORIST
PICKING THROUGH MY REFUSE.

06:16.977 --> 06:20.080
THIS WAS THE THIRD TIME
I'D CAUGHT HER ON MY PROPERTY.

06:20.113 --> 06:23.016
- AND THIS TIME YOU MADE YOUR
PROBLEM GO AWAY PERMANENTLY?

06:23.050 --> 06:26.520
- THAT WAS THE PLAN.
I CALLED THE POLICE.

06:26.554 --> 06:28.622
- THERE'S NO RECORD OF HER
BEING ARRESTED THAT NIGHT.

06:28.656 --> 06:31.158
- SHE TOOK OFF RUNNING
BEFORE THEY GOT THERE,

06:31.191 --> 06:34.662
SCREECHING ABOUT HOW
MY CARBON FOOTPRINT WAS SO BIG

06:34.695 --> 06:36.964
THERE WERE PLENTY OF PLACES
TO FIND DIRT ON ME.

06:36.997 --> 06:39.032
- COULD SHE HAVE GONE DIGGING
IN YOUR DUMPSTER

06:39.066 --> 06:40.634
HERE AT GLOBE OIL?

06:40.668 --> 06:44.104
- CHECK WITH SECURITY.
AND BUGGER OFF.

06:44.137 --> 06:46.006
- GLOBE OIL DOESN'T HAVE
A SECURITY CAMERA

06:46.039 --> 06:47.475
IN THE GARBAGE AREA.

06:47.508 --> 06:49.610
BUT A TIMES SQUARE CAM'S
AT 49TH AND BROADWAY.

06:49.643 --> 06:52.112
- RIGHT ACROSS THE STREET FROM
GLOBE OIL'S CORPORATE OFFICES.

06:52.145 --> 06:54.982
- AND THERE SHE IS.

06:55.015 --> 06:58.018
ONE HOUR AFTER LEAVING
NICHOLAS TURNER'S HOME.

06:58.051 --> 07:00.588
- AND THAT'S WHEN OUR PERP
ARRIVED IN HIS VOLVO.

07:00.621 --> 07:04.057
- UNFORTUNATELY, HIS CAR BLOCKS
OUR VIEW OF THE ATTACK.

07:04.091 --> 07:05.192
FAST FORWARD.

07:05.225 --> 07:06.560
[click]

07:08.496 --> 07:09.797
Benson: HE BLITZED HER.

07:09.830 --> 07:11.098
HE THREW HER IN THE BACK

07:11.131 --> 07:12.933
AND TOOK OFF
WITHOUT ANYBODY SEEING IT.

07:12.966 --> 07:15.068
- PERP HAD BALLS
DOING IT IN THE OPEN.

07:15.102 --> 07:16.103
HE'S DONE THIS BEFORE.

07:16.136 --> 07:18.739
- OH, SAME GUY, SAME CAR,
SAME HAT AND HOODIE

07:18.772 --> 07:20.240
SHOWS UP TWO DAYS LATER
AT MERCY HOSPITAL,

07:20.273 --> 07:22.175
AND HE DUMPS SAM'S BODY
IN THAT LAUNDRY CART.

07:22.209 --> 07:24.044
- WE GET A PLATE THIS TIME?

07:24.077 --> 07:26.079
- YEAH, FIN'S RUNNING IT.
- WE HIT A DEAD END.

07:26.113 --> 07:28.916
CAR'S REGISTERED
TO A THOMAS GAMBEL, 64.

07:28.949 --> 07:32.085
HE LIVED IN BROOKLYN UNTIL
HE DIED NINE MONTHS AGO.

07:34.021 --> 07:35.756
- HEY, NEED A HAND?

07:35.789 --> 07:37.891
- I GOT IT, THANKS.

07:37.925 --> 07:40.761
- THOMAS GAMBEL?
HE LIVED HERE?

07:40.794 --> 07:43.597
- YEAH, I'M HIS SON, JASON.

07:43.631 --> 07:45.198
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

07:45.232 --> 07:47.535
- THE VOLVO WAGON
STILL REGISTERED TO HIM.

07:47.568 --> 07:48.936
- I ONLY INHERITED THE HOUSE.

07:48.969 --> 07:51.772
MY...BROTHER, HENRY,
GOT THE CAR.

07:51.805 --> 07:53.206
- HENRY.
WHERE CAN WE FIND HIM?

07:53.240 --> 07:55.042
- HE WAS THE BLACK SHEEP
OF THE FAMILY.

07:55.075 --> 07:56.844
WE HAVEN'T STAYED IN TOUCH.

07:56.877 --> 08:00.013
I HAVE HIS ADDRESS INSIDE.
LET ME GET IT FOR YOU.

08:02.315 --> 08:03.784
[lock clicks]

08:03.817 --> 08:06.119
- DID HE JUST LOCK US OUT?

08:06.153 --> 08:08.088
[jiggling doorknob]

08:08.121 --> 08:10.223
- OKAY.
MR. GAMBEL?

08:10.257 --> 08:11.792
OPEN THE DOOR.

08:11.825 --> 08:14.027
[gunshots]

08:14.061 --> 08:16.997
- SVU PORTABLE TO CENTRAL.
10-13.

08:17.030 --> 08:18.265
SHOTS FIRED.

08:18.298 --> 08:22.736
REQUEST BACKUP
AT 435 CARLTON AVENUE.

08:27.174 --> 08:29.509
- GAMBEL, FREEZE!

08:41.989 --> 08:43.857
- YOU CRACKED MY HEAD OPEN!

08:43.891 --> 08:45.158
- 'CAUSE YOU
TRIED TO BLOW OURS OFF!

08:45.192 --> 08:46.760
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

08:46.794 --> 08:48.161
FOR THE ATTEMPTED MURDER
OF A POLICE OFFICER.

08:48.195 --> 08:50.698
- LET'S SEE
WHAT'S IN YOUR LITTLE BOX.

08:50.731 --> 08:53.967
A BRACELET
MADE OUT OF BOTTLE CAPS.

08:54.001 --> 08:55.836
THIS LOOKS LIKE
SAMANTHA'S WORK.

08:55.869 --> 08:58.672
- YEAH, COULDN'T LEAVE YOUR
RAPE TROPHIES BEHIND?

08:58.706 --> 09:00.240
- SAM WAS A TREE HUGGER.

09:00.273 --> 09:03.777
I DON'T THINK SHE'D BE WEARING
ANYTHING MADE OUT OF IVORY.

09:03.811 --> 09:06.614
SHE WAS SINGLE, SO THIS
ISN'T HER ENGAGEMENT RING.

09:06.647 --> 09:09.049
I BET IT'S NOT HER BROOCH,
EITHER...

09:09.082 --> 09:10.818
OR HER LACE HANDKERCHIEF.

09:12.720 --> 09:14.287
- ALL THESE FROM
YOUR DIFFERENT VICTIMS?

09:16.924 --> 09:20.093
- SON OF A BITCH
IS A SERIAL KILLER.

09:23.931 --> 09:26.366
- WE GOT YOU ON
SAMANTHA MILLERTON'S MURDER.

09:26.399 --> 09:27.935
SEE, OUR LAB FOUND
HER FINGERPRINT

09:27.968 --> 09:30.170
ON ONE OF
THESE BOTTLE CAPS.

09:30.203 --> 09:32.339
- WHO DID YOU KILL
FOR THAT ONE?

09:32.372 --> 09:34.875
- THIS ONE LOOKS LIKE IT BELONGS
TO A LITTLE OLD LADY.

09:34.908 --> 09:39.112
IS THAT HER LACE HANKY, TOO?

09:39.146 --> 09:41.014
DO YOU LIKE DIDDLING GRANDMAS?

09:41.048 --> 09:43.316
- "ALAN AND JOAN FOREVER."

09:43.350 --> 09:45.318
YOU MADE SURE
THAT DIDN'T HAPPEN.

09:45.352 --> 09:46.920
- I DIDN'T KILL ANYONE.

09:46.954 --> 09:48.121
- WELL, YOU DID
A PRETTY GOOD JOB

09:48.155 --> 09:49.790
TRYING TO TAKE US OUT
WITH YOUR .357.

09:49.823 --> 09:52.025
- YOU SHOULD HAVE DONE A BETTER
JOB STASHING SAM'S BODY.

09:52.059 --> 09:53.961
YOU SEE, THAT, WITH YOUR
LITTLE TROPHY COLLECTION,

09:53.994 --> 09:56.063
IS GOING TO GIVE YOU
THE DEATH PENALTY.

09:56.096 --> 09:57.998
- NEW YORK STATE DOESN'T
EXECUTE PEOPLE ANYMORE.

09:58.031 --> 10:00.033
- HEY, KNOW-IT-ALL,
YOU COULD STILL BE CHARGED

10:00.067 --> 10:01.101
WITH A CAPITAL CRIME,

10:01.134 --> 10:03.270
EVEN WITH THE LEGISLATIVE
MORATORIUM IN EFFECT.

10:03.303 --> 10:05.072
- YOU NEVER KNOW WHEN
THEY'RE GONNA LIFT IT.

10:05.105 --> 10:07.841
ONE DAY YOU'RE GROWING OLD
ON DEATH ROW...

10:07.875 --> 10:10.844
AND THE NEXT DAY YOU'RE SIZZLING
LIKE A PIECE OF BACON.

10:10.878 --> 10:12.112
- OKAY.

10:12.145 --> 10:14.081
GAMBEL, DO YOURSELF A FAVOR.

10:14.114 --> 10:17.017
TELL US EVERYTHING, AND
THE D.A. WILL CUT YOU A DEAL.

10:21.955 --> 10:24.124
YOU WANT TO ROT IN PRISON
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE?

10:24.157 --> 10:25.358
YOU GOT IT!

10:25.392 --> 10:27.928
- YOU CAN'T PUT ME
BACK IN PRISON!

10:27.961 --> 10:30.030
NO, THESE THINGS AREN'T MINE!

10:30.063 --> 10:32.132
- SO YOU JUST HAPPENED
TO FIND A BRACELET

10:32.165 --> 10:33.867
BELONGING TO A MURDER VICTIM

10:33.901 --> 10:35.803
WHOSE BODY WAS THROWN
FROM YOUR CAR?

10:35.836 --> 10:37.170
- I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT ANYTHING.

10:37.204 --> 10:39.072
- I'VE GOT FIVE TROPHIES
RIGHT HERE,

10:39.106 --> 10:41.975
AND WE'RE GONNA
FIND THESE WOMEN.

10:42.009 --> 10:45.746
MAKE IT EASY ON YOURSELF.
JUST GIVE US THE NAMES.

10:48.115 --> 10:49.249
[knock at door]

10:49.282 --> 10:52.820
- YOU GOT A MINUTE,
DETECTIVES?

11:03.030 --> 11:04.932
WHAT THE HELL'S GOING ON?

11:04.965 --> 11:06.767
YOU KNOW YOU CAN'T
INTERVIEW A PERP

11:06.800 --> 11:08.468
WHO JUST TRIED TO KILL YOU.

11:08.501 --> 11:11.071
- BELIEVE ME,
HE'S NOT A THREAT NOW.

11:11.104 --> 11:12.372
- YOU PUNISH HIM
BY CRACKING HIS SKULL?

11:12.405 --> 11:13.741
- HE GOT THAT
DURING THE CHASE.

11:13.774 --> 11:15.375
SERIOUSLY, CAPTAIN,
WE'RE GOOD.

11:15.408 --> 11:17.945
- YOU ARE NOT
CLEARED FOR DUTY

11:17.978 --> 11:20.981
UNTIL YOU SEE DR. WONG
FOR YOUR MANDATORY PSYCH EVALS.

11:21.014 --> 11:24.051
- CAPTAIN, THAT PISSANT
IS ABOUT TO POP.

11:24.084 --> 11:25.919
- WELL, FIN
IS GOING TO DO THE POPPING.

11:25.953 --> 11:28.421
- SORRY, GUYS.

11:31.925 --> 11:33.927
WANNABE COP KILLER, HUH?

11:33.961 --> 11:36.263
CAME A LONG WAY
FROM EMBEZZLEMENT.

11:38.165 --> 11:41.068
SAYS HERE YOU DID
