I RAN YOUR DNA AGAINST MINE.

36:38.897 --> 36:41.400
BUT, VIVIAN,
I'M STILL HERE FOR YOU.

36:41.433 --> 36:43.235
- COME ON.
GO TO HELL!

36:43.269 --> 36:45.404
GO TO HELL.
COME ON.

36:45.437 --> 36:46.572
- CALVIN.

37:00.286 --> 37:02.921
- UNI SAID BURLOCK WENT IN
AT 5:00 P.M. YESTERDAY.

37:02.954 --> 37:05.424
HASN'T LEFT SINCE.

37:05.457 --> 37:08.260
- FIN'S GOT EYES ON GAMBEL
AT A LOCAL HOTEL.

37:09.861 --> 37:11.963
- KICKING A GUY
OUT OF HIS OWN HOUSE?

37:11.997 --> 37:15.667
SAYS A LOT ABOUT THE HOLD
BURLOCK HAS OVER HIM.

37:15.701 --> 37:17.836
Fin: GAMBEL'S ON HIS WAY
BACK HOME.

37:17.869 --> 37:20.372
COMING AROUND THE CORNER.
- WELL, WELL, WELL.

37:20.406 --> 37:21.773
EITHER BURLOCK
ORDERED HIM HERE

37:21.807 --> 37:23.309
OR GAMBEL SUDDENLY
GREW A PAIR.

37:23.342 --> 37:25.777
THIS SHOULD BE INTERESTING.

37:35.521 --> 37:37.456
- YOU THINK BURLOCK
CALLED GAMBEL

37:37.489 --> 37:39.291
TO GO ON THE PROWL AGAIN?

37:39.325 --> 37:41.660
- WELL, WHEN YOU GET THE ITCH,
YOU CALL YOUR BITCH.

37:44.596 --> 37:46.598
- WELL, I HOPE
THEY LEAVE SOON.

37:46.632 --> 37:49.635
I CAN'T WAIT
TO PUT BURLOCK AWAY.

37:59.378 --> 38:00.979
- GAMBEL, DON'T MOVE.

38:01.012 --> 38:02.381
DON'T MOVE.

38:06.618 --> 38:08.754
- HE'S DEAD.
THERE'S BLOOD EVERYWHERE.

38:08.787 --> 38:11.022
- WELL, THANKS
FOR HELPING US OUT.

38:13.124 --> 38:15.327
- ARREST HIM FOR THE MURDER
OF WALTER BURLOCK.

38:15.361 --> 38:16.862
- LOOKS LIKE
YOU WHACKED HIM GOOD.

38:19.631 --> 38:22.734
- BLOOD SPATTER LOOKS LIKE
GAMBEL BLITZED HIM.

38:24.536 --> 38:26.905
- DEFINITELY HIT HIM WITH
THE CAST IRON MORE THAN ONCE.

38:26.938 --> 38:30.909
LOT OF RAGE.
- GAMBEL FITS THAT DESCRIPTION.

38:33.044 --> 38:35.581
- WHO YOU TRYING TO KID, LIV?
LOOK AT THE BLOOD.

38:35.614 --> 38:37.683
IT'S CONGEALED,
BEGINNING TO CRUST.

38:37.716 --> 38:39.485
THAT BODY HAS BEEN THERE
FOR HOURS.

38:39.518 --> 38:42.554
- NO. VIVIAN
COULDN'T HAVE DONE THIS.

38:42.588 --> 38:44.089
HER FIRST PRIORITY IS CALVIN.

38:44.122 --> 38:46.925
- DOESN'T MEAN SHE COULDN'T
HAVE COME OVER HERE LAST NIGHT.

38:46.958 --> 38:49.561
- GAMBEL COULD HAVE
LEFT HIS HOTEL UNNOTICED,

38:49.595 --> 38:50.696
COME BACK HERE, KILLED HIM,

38:50.729 --> 38:52.898
AND THEN COME BACK HERE TODAY
TO DISCOVER THE BODY.

38:52.931 --> 38:55.066
- OR VIVIAN FOLLOWED
BURLOCK HOME,

38:55.100 --> 38:56.201
BATTED HER EYELASHES,

38:56.234 --> 38:59.471
AND THEN BATTED HIM WITH
THE FIRST THING THAT SHE SAW...

38:59.505 --> 39:01.373
A PAN ON THE STOVE.

39:06.044 --> 39:08.447
[doorbell chiming]

39:10.916 --> 39:12.150
- I'M LOOKING FOR
VIVIAN ARLISS.

39:12.183 --> 39:15.086
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?
- UH, TO TALK TO HER.

39:15.120 --> 39:16.154
IS SHE HOME?
- NO.

39:16.187 --> 39:17.556
- AND YOU ARE...

39:17.589 --> 39:18.890
- I'M SARAH HOYT,
FRIEND OF VIV'S.

39:18.924 --> 39:20.058
I'VE BEEN HELPING HER OUT.

39:20.091 --> 39:22.661
I DON'T KNOW WHERE SHE WENT
OR WHEN SHE'S COMING BACK.

39:22.694 --> 39:25.497
- PLEASE HAVE HER CALL
DETECTIVE BENSON IMMEDIATELY.

39:25.531 --> 39:26.765
IT'S VERY IMPORTANT.

39:32.938 --> 39:34.406
- LET ME GUESS.
VIVIAN WASN'T HOME.

39:34.440 --> 39:36.041
- WHY, DID SHE CALL?

39:36.074 --> 39:38.944
- NO. AND SHE'S NOT GOING TO.
- HOW DO YOU KNOW?

39:41.713 --> 39:44.182
- GOT HERE ABOUT
AN HOUR AGO.

39:44.215 --> 39:47.786
THE ONLY THING HE'LL SAY IS
HE'S GOT SOMETHING TO GIVE YOU.

39:51.590 --> 39:53.792
- WHAT'S GOING ON, CALVIN?

39:55.461 --> 39:59.164
WHAT HAPPENED?

39:59.197 --> 40:01.767
- MY MOM'S GONE.

40:03.535 --> 40:06.171
- DO YOU KNOW WHERE SHE WENT?

40:06.204 --> 40:08.607
- NO.

40:09.941 --> 40:11.176
- SO HOW DID YOU GET HERE?

40:11.209 --> 40:13.445
- MY MOM DROVE ME.

40:14.980 --> 40:18.216
SHE TOLD ME TO RUN IN
AND GIVE THIS TO YOU.

40:18.249 --> 40:20.952
AND WHEN YOU WEREN'T HERE,
I WENT OUT TO TELL HER,

40:20.986 --> 40:23.054
AND SHE WAS GONE.

40:25.090 --> 40:28.860
HOW COULD SHE LEAVE ME HERE?

40:28.894 --> 40:31.797
- I DON'T KNOW, HONEY,
BUT WE'LL FIND HER.

40:31.830 --> 40:33.799
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

40:36.001 --> 40:37.469
- NO, IT'S NOT.

40:39.037 --> 40:41.039
- CAN I SEE
WHAT'S IN THE ENVELOPE?

41:10.769 --> 41:12.971
- WHAT IS IT?

41:13.004 --> 41:18.977
- IT'S A NOTARIZED
TRANSFER OF PARENTAL RIGHTS.

41:19.010 --> 41:22.514
VIVIAN MADE ME CALVIN'S
LEGAL GUARDIAN.

